      Given <math|A\<in\>S<rsub|n>>, where <math|S<rsub|n>> is the set of <math|n>-dimensional positive-definite matrices

      <\equation*>
        A\<cdot\>x<rsub|e><above|=|rep>Q\<Lambda\>Q<rsup|T>\<cdot\>x<rsub|e>.
      </equation*>
    </theorem>
